<!-- partials/banInfoModal.ejs -->
<div class="modal fade" id="banInfoModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="banInfoModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
   <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
      <div class="modal-content">
         <div class="modal-header bg-danger text-white">
            <h5 class="modal-title fw-bold" id="banInfoModalLabel">
               <i class="fas fa-gavel me-2"></i>
               Ban Management Guide
            </h5>
            <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
         </div>
         <div class="modal-body">
            <div class="alert alert-danger mb-4">
               <h4 class="alert-heading d-flex align-items-center">
                  <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
                  About Ban System
               </h4>
               <hr>
               <p class="mb-0">This interface allows you to manage user bans with various durations and reasons. Bans affect user access immediately and require service restart to take full effect.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card border-danger mb-4">
               <div class="card-header bg-light">
                  <i class="fas fa-columns me-2"></i> Ban Process Explanation
               </div>
               <div class="card-body">
                  <div class="row">
                     <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card border-danger h-100">
                           <div class="card-header bg-danger bg-opacity-10 text-danger">
                              <i class="fas fa-clock me-2"></i> Timing
                           </div>
                           <div class="card-body">
                              <ul class="mb-0">
                                 <li><strong>Immediate Effect:</strong> User will be disconnected within 1 minute</li>
                                 <li><strong>Service Restart:</strong> BanSrv restarts automatically (3 minutes)</li>
                                 <li><strong>Full Activation:</strong> Ban becomes fully active after restart</li>
                              </ul>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                     <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card border-warning h-100">
                           <div class="card-header bg-warning bg-opacity-10 text-warning">
                              <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle me-2"></i> Restrictions
                           </div>
                           <div class="card-body">
                              <ul class="mb-0">
                                 <li><strong>During Restart:</strong> No new bans can be added</li>
                                 <li><strong>Permanent Bans:</strong> Require manual removal</li>
                                 <li><strong>Temporary Bans:</strong> Automatically expire</li>
                              </ul>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card border-danger mb-4">
               <div class="card-header bg-light">
                  <i class="fas fa-user-circle me-2"></i> User Notification
               </div>
               <div class="card-body">
                  <p>After a game account is blocked, a corresponding ban notification will automatically appear on the user's profile page on the website.</p>
                  <div class="alert alert-info mt-3">
                     <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>
                     The notification includes ban details such as duration, reason, and expiration date (for temporary bans).
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card border-danger mb-4">
               <div class="card-header bg-light">
                  <i class="fas fa-tools me-2"></i> Available Actions
               </div>
               <div class="card-body">
                  <div class="row">
                     <div class="col-md-4 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                        <div class="card h-100">
                           <div class="card-header bg-danger bg-opacity-10 text-danger">
                              <i class="fas fa-ban me-2"></i> Add Ban
                           </div>
                           <div class="card-body">
                              <p>Apply temporary or permanent ban with specified reason. User will be disconnected.</p>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                     <div class="col-md-4 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                        <div class="card h-100">
                           <div class="card-header bg-warning bg-opacity-10 text-warning">
                              <i class="fas fa-user-slash me-2"></i> Kick User
                           </div>
                           <div class="card-body">
                              <p>Immediately disconnect user without applying any ban restrictions.</p>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                     <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="card h-100">
                           <div class="card-header bg-success bg-opacity-10 text-success">
                              <i class="fas fa-unlock me-2"></i> Unban
                           </div>
                           <div class="card-body">
                              <p>Remove active ban before its expiration date. Requires service restart.</p>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="alert alert-warning">
               <h5 class="alert-heading d-flex align-items-center">
                  <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
                  Important Notes
               </h5>
               <hr>
               <ul class="mb-0">
                  <li>BanSrv restart takes approximately 3 minutes</li>
                  <li>During restart, ban management functions are unavailable</li>
                  <li>Permanent bans remain until manually removed</li>
                  <li>Always verify user identity before applying bans</li>
               </ul>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" data-bs-dismiss="modal">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-1"></i> Understood
            </button>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>
</div>